                    → выгрузка в Вашу систему.
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-4 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-slate-200 bg-slate-100">
                  <div class="video-poster-shell relative aspect-video w-full bg-slate-950">
                    <button
